de.hlu.ust
Class TableData

java.lang.Object
  de.hlu.ust.TableData

public class TableData
extends java.lang.Object

A little bit support to create HTML table data tags and HTML colorize numbers. Most functionality is given by the static methods.

colorize

public static java.lang.String colorize(java.lang.String str)
Surround the given number with an HTML font tag in dependency of a number sign.
  • Gives minus signed numbers red.
  • Gives plus signed numbers green.
  • Gives zeros values gray.
  • Convertes "+-" to "-".
  • Convertes "--" to "+".

Parameters:
str - The input string with a possible sign.
Returns:
HTML tagged output string.
